                            teil</add> leypgedings, das sie von ew <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        iren teil leipgedings volgen lassen wöllet. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>ascens<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan>.</ab>
